 um information community to generate research ideas and accelerate innovat
 ion.\nDetails:\nDate: Friday\, April 24\nTime: 9:00am-4:00pm (CT)\nLocatio
 n: Ryan Hall | Room 4003\nRSVP: Register here\nThe symposium will feature 
